data.title: Chelsea Clinton Looks To Help Her Family Return To The White House
data.meta_description: The once shy preteen is now a mother of two who has become one of her mother's closest political advisers. On Thursday night, she'll introduce Hillary Clinton as she accepts the Democratic nomination.
